data.description: Here is a great opportunity to have your own hunting cabin in Nelson County, your own private weekend retreat, or your own short term rental after verifying zoning use by the county. Easy walking distance to the Tye River which is stocked from October-May with trout. Finished living area is estimated from an exterior measurement of the footprint of the home. Buyer's and their agents are to verify all information contained in this listing deemed necessary to prepare an offer.
